Syntax: aura <*aura name*|off|stop>

The deikhan's aura is the manefestation of the favor she enjoys with her deities. 
Auras are the deities reaching out and shaping the deikhan, and by extension her group.
Deikhans are the chosen tools of deities in this world and as such, these auras don'the
require any prayers or demonstrations of piety. They are simply part of the bond between
diety and the Deikhan.

See Also: AURA OF MIGHT, AURA OF REGENERATION, AURA OF VENGEANCE, AURA OF ABSOLUTION, AURA OF THE GUARDIAN
